<html>
<head>
<title>Univent - College Event Portal</title>

<style>

body {
    background-color: #f0fdf4;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

.header {
    color: white;
    background-color: #059669;         
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
}

.footer {
    color: white;
    background-color: #059669;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
}

.nav {
    background-color: #065f46;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 15px;
}

.nav a {
    color: #d1fae5;
    margin: 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.nav a:hover {
    color: #facc15;
}

.container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.card {
    background-color: white;
    width: 320px;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.profile-img {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 4px solid #059669;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

section h3 {
    text-align: center;
}

#education p {
    text-align: center;
}

#hobby ul {
    text-align: left;
    margin-left: 40px;
}

.button,
button {
    background-color: #facc15;        
    border-radius: 15px;
    width: 110px;
    height: 40px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #047857;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

.footer a {
    color: #d1fae5;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 10px;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="header">
    <h2>Univent - College Event Portal</h2>
    <p>
        Welcome to Univent, your hub for college clubs and events. Explore our clubs,
        register for activities, and stay updated with upcoming events.
    </p>
</header>

<nav class="nav">
    <a href="#sports">Sports Club</a>
    <a href="#tech">Tech Club</a>
    <a href="#arts">Arts Club</a>
</nav>

<main>
<section id="sports">
    <h3>Sports Club</h3>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">

            <img src="https://c8.alamy.com/comp/C8T3X1/illustration-of-sports-club-C8T3X1.jpg" 
            alt="Sports Club" class="profile-img">
            
            <h4>Play, Compete, Grow!</h4>

            <p>
                Join our Sports Club to participate in tournaments, training sessions, and inter‑college matches. 
                All sports lovers are welcome to register and build their skills and teamwork.
            </p>
            
            <button>Register</button>

            <div>&#x2709; sports@univentcollege.edu</div>
            <div>&#x260E; +91-9876543210</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section><br><br>

<section id="tech">
    <h3>Tech Club</h3>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">

            <img src="https://tse3.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.x5Aj_BOSIwXChx1Z1z4uQgHaEw?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3" 
            alt="Tech Club" class="profile-img">

            <h4>Innovate, Code, Create!</h4>

            <p>
                Our Tech Club organizes coding hackathons, workshops, and project exhibitions.
                Join us to sharpen your technical skills and contribute to real‑world solutions.
            </p>

            <button>Register</button>

            <div>&#x2709; tech@univentcollege.edu</div>
            <div>&#x260E; +91-8765432109</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section><br><br>

<section id="arts">
    <h3>Arts Club</h3>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">

            <img src="https://tse1.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.UeU5o0lvnyzklWC647B_SwHaH0?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3" 
            alt="Arts Club" class="profile-img">

            <h4>Express, Create, Inspire!</h4>

            <p>
                The Arts Club brings together painters, musicians, dancers, and designers. 
                Join us to showcase your talent in cultural events and creative festivals.
            </p>

            <button>Register</button>

            <div>&#x2709; arts@univentcollege.edu</div>
            <div>&#x260E; +91-7654321098</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</main><br><br>

<footer class="footer">
    <h2>&copy; Univent College Events Portal</h2>

    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/">Facebook</a>
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/">Instagram</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a>

    <br><br>

    <button class="button">Add Event (Council)</button>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
